page.title: 20CONTRIBUTORS
page.content: This survey was carried out by Class 2 at The Richard Clarke First School, Abbots Bromley, Staffordshire. We enjoyed working on this project throughout the summer term and talked to many interesting people during the course of the investigation. Those involved were Jamie Bradbury, Colin Fowell, Daniel Meads, Stuart Morton, James Ray, Matthew Thomas,Lucy Aldridge, Sarah Baker, Jo-Anne Barker, Jennette Gosling, Tracy Hampson, Sally Henry, Catherine Joynes, Louis Knight, Alison Maddox, Joanna Rees, Victoria Roe, Claire Singer, Abigail Taylor, Julie Turner and Shirley Wheeler. Mr W.S. Wheeler took the slides.
